<br>
From all reports, /shield is the command, it lasts 12 seconds, has a 3 minute reuse timer, and is available to any warrior over level 30.<br>
<br>
Found more details of it on <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessage?topicID=2238.topic">The Steel Warrior &gt; The Arena &gt; /shield is live</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br>
<br>
